Query should be able to get public keys of sub CAs and CAs via certificates

CRL
2 States 
    : Revoked - revocation can not be undone e.g ca pk leaked
    : Hold - reversible temporary invalidity, pk lost etc
Reason
    : unspecified
    : keyCompromise
    : cACompromise
    : affiliationChanged
    : superseded
    : cessationOfOperation
    : certificateHold
    : removeFromCRL
    : privilegeWithdrawn
    : aACompromise




Function
    Revoke 
    UnRevoke
